Class MockProvisionerTenantStore

java.lang.Object
  co.cask.coopr.provisioner.mock.MockProvisionerTenantStore

public class MockProvisionerTenantStore
extends Object

Mock in memory store for keeping track of how many workers each tenant should have as well as how many workers each tenant has live.
